<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Inditronics Meter Management Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
    
    :root {
      --primary: #5046e5;
      --primary-light: #eef2ff;
      --success: #10b981;
      --warning: #f59e0b;
      --dark: #111827;
      --gray: #6b7280;
      --light-gray: #f3f4f6;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--dark);
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    
    .email-header {
      background-color: var(--primary);
      position: relative;
      height: 120px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .header-pattern {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      opacity: 0.1;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='100' height='100' viewBox='0 0 100 100' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M11 18c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm48 25c3.866 0 7-3.134 7-7s-3.134-7-7-7-7 3.134-7 7 3.134 7 7 7zm-43-7c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zm63 31c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zM34 90c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zm56-76c1.657 0 3-1.343 3-3s-1.343-3-3-3-3 1.343-3 3 1.343 3 3 3zM12 86c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm28-65c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm23-11c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm-6 60c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm29 22c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zM32 63c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm57-13c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5-5 2.24-5 5 2.24 5 5 5zm-9-21c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM60 91c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM35 41c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2zM12 60c1.105 0 2-.895 2-2s-.895-2-2-2-2 .895-2 2 .895 2 2 2z' fill='%23ffffff' fill-opacity='1' fill-rule='evenodd'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    }
    
    .logo-container {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 30px;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: 10;
    }
    
    .logo-text {
      color: white;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    
    .logo-subtitle {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .email-body {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .card-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-top: -60px;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .card-header {
      padding: 24px 30px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    
    .card-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .card-subtitle {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .card-body {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    
    .welcome-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      color: var(--dark);
    }
    
    .credentials-section {
      background-color: var(--primary-light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .credentials-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      color: var(--primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }
    
    .credentials-title svg {
      margin-right: 6px;
    }
    
    .credential-item {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    
    .credential-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .credential-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--gray);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    
    .credential-value {
      background-color: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--dark);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(80, 70, 229, 0.3);
    }
    
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #4338ca;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(80, 70, 229, 0.4);
    }
    
    .expiry-alert {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--warning);
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    
    .expiry-alert svg {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-right: 12px;
      fill: var(--warning);
    }
    
    .expiry-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9a3412;
    }
    
    .help-text {
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background-color: var(--border);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .email-footer {
      padding: 20px 30px;
      background-color: var(--light-gray);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--gray);
    }
    
    .footer-text {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    
    .footer-text:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .email-body {
        padding: 30px 15px;
      }
      
      .card-header, .card-body {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      
      .logo-container {
        left: 15px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <div class="header-pattern"></div>
      <div class="logo-container">
        <div class="logo-text">INDITRONICS</div>
        <div class="logo-subtitle">Meter Management</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="email-body">
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h1 class="card-title">Account Created</h1>
          <p class="card-subtitle">Your dashboard access is ready</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="welcome-text">Hello {{firstname}}, your account for the Inditronics Meter Management Dashboard has been created. Please use the credentials below to access your account.</p>
          
          <div class="credentials-section">
            <div class="credentials-title">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
              </svg>
              Your Access Credentials
            </div>
            
            <div class="credential-item">
              <div class="credential-label">Email Address</div>
              <div class="credential-value">{{email}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="credential-item">
              <div class="credential-label">Temporary Password</div>
              <div class="credential-value">{{tempPassword}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="credential-item">
              <div class="credential-label">One-Time Password (OTP)</div>
              <div class="credential-value">{{otp}}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="button-container">
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Activate Your Account</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="expiry-alert">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"></path>
            </svg>
            <div class="expiry-text">This activation link and OTP will expire in 7 days.</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="help-text">
            <p>After activation, you'll be prompted to set a new password and complete your profile setup.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="divider"></div>
          
          <div class="help-text">
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your system administrator.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p class="footer-text">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p class="footer-text">© 2025 Inditronics. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="footer-text">Smart Meter Solutions • Secure • Reliable</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>